OL,4,G0435FFour in a Bed
OL,5,     GThe third visit is to the Dolphin
OL,6,     GHotel in Exmouth, Devon, where
OL,7,     Gowner Jo takes her guests
OL,8,     Gpaintballing and to a floating
OL,9,     Grestaurant. But there are
OL,10,     Gsuspicions of game-playing.
OL,11,G0500FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GPat and Nigel pride themselves on
OL,13,     Gtheir award-winning breakfast at
OL,14,     Gtheir B&B in Seaton, Devon. But
OL,15,     Gwill an afternoon spent town-
OL,16,     Gcrying entertain their guests?
OL,17,G0525FFour in a Bed
OL,18,     GWith all the visits over, the
OL,19,     GB&Bers come together to confront
OL,20,     Gtheir rivals and discover how
OL,21,     Gmuch they've been paid, before
OL,22,     Gthe winner is announced.
